  "text": "[6] Various MVA techniques are presented by [CITATION_1] where they are applied to analyze data obtained by the Cluster spacecraft at the magnetopause. The MVA methods they present differ in the number of data types input to the analysis (i.e., by augmenting IMF data by using three dimensional plasma velocity data, etc.) or in the type of constraints imposed on the variance matrices analyzed. Several of the MVA techniques employed by Sonnerup et al.",
